'''聖瑪麗山'''<ref>Bratina Jurkovič, Nataša. 2014. "[http://urbani-izziv.uirs.si/Portals/uizziv/papers/urbani-izziv-en-2014-25-01-003.pdf Perception, Experience and the Use of Public Urban Spaces by Residents of Urban Neighbourhoods]". ''Urbani izziv'' 25(1): 107–125, p. 117.</ref>（{{lang-sl|Šmarna gora}}，{{lang-de|Großkahlenberg}}<ref>''Laibach'' (map, 1:75,000). 1918. Vienna: K.u.k. Militärgeographisches Institut.</ref>）是位於[[斯洛維尼亞|斯洛維尼亞]]首都[[盧比安納|盧比安納]]北郊的一座[[山|山]]峰。聖瑪麗山是盧比安納的最高峰，也是一個受歡迎的遠足地點<ref name="Geopedia2012-01-30">{{cite web |url=http://geopedia.si/#T105_L410_F10110084_x459056_y109604_s15_b4 |title=Settlements: Ljubljana |publisher=Geopedia.si |accessdate=30 January 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.burger.si/SmarnaGora/uvod_ENG.html |title=Šmarna gora |work=Slovenia-Landmarks |first=Boštjan |last=Burger |accessdate=30 January 2012}}</ref>。山下有數個村莊。
